  "introductionSummary": "Learn what Twingl Road does and how to use it on the road.",
  "introductionBody": "Twingl Road is an audio-first travel guide for the road. As you pass through cities and towns, it introduces local history, landmarks, scenery, food, festivals, and notable people in a cinematic documentary style.\n\nUse Start Guiding when you want the app to automatically introduce each new town as you enter it. Use Check This Town when you want a one-time guide for your current location without continuous monitoring.\n\nThe Magazine tab gives you related links for the current area. Place links open in Maps, while people, events, and cultural references open in browser search.\n\nIn More, you can choose the narration persona, check the current system language, and select a premium or enhanced TTS voice. On iOS, matching Settings > Apple Intelligence & Siri > Language with the app language can help local AI narration work more naturally.",
